{"tid":2232271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：不容許港獨議題滲入校園　必需要揪出害群之馬","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T12:14:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1f18380f126c6a0fdb5f28d1b21a400ccbddc43d","tid":2232271,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553310-20201006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553310-20201006.htm&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=8b5fcf2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553310-20201006.htm&h=75a28a51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553310-20201006.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b38182269655e76511105ab69d0dd2a9f34d240c","tid":2232271,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>楊潤雄：涉專業失德被取消教師註冊罕見　坊間說法扭曲局方專業判斷</strong><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄表示，今次是首宗涉及專業失德而取消註冊的個案，形容是罕見，強調本屆政府重視教育，投入大量資源，但同時責無旁貸有把關及監管責任，目標是維持一支專業及受社會信任的教師團隊。 <br />\n<br />\n他認為，坊間有說法扭曲教育局的專業判斷，需要作出澄清，重申本屆政府依法辦事，維持程序公義，以學生的長遠利益為依歸，不容許港獨及違法意識在學校蔓延。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2360396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2360396&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f35fc5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2360396</a>"},{"pid":"6eabf9405f42cf5718fd0b88ccab7fef52abaed1","tid":2232271,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKGQmH2.jpg&amp;h=aec3874b&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"18624e49a44d09c68c373c5c37f45300c735ff71","tid":2232271,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"